  "text": "Bactericidal activity of linenscin OC2. None of the gramnegative strains tested was inhibited by the crude linenscin OC2 preparation, whereas all gram-positive bacteria were sensitive, with similar responses to the substance, except L. lactis CNRZ 1076, which was more sensitive (Table 1) . Like many of the bacteriocins produced by lactic acid bacteria [CITATION_1] , linenscin OC2 has a broad spectrum of activity.",
